sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Runtime as Caikit Runtime<br/>8085/TCP gRPC<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>TLS optional
    participant TextGenLocal as TextGeneration<br/>(Local Module)
    participant TextGenTGIS as TextGenerationTGIS<br/>(TGIS Module)
    participant TGIS as TGIS Backend<br/>8033/TCP gRPC<br/>TLS/mTLS optional
    participant EmbedMod as EmbeddingModule<br/>(Local)
    participant PeftTrain as PeftPromptTuning<br/>(Training)
    participant TorchDist as PyTorch Distributed<br/>29550/TCP
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 1: Local Text Generation Inference

    Client->>Runtime: POST /api/v1/task/text-generation<br/>or gRPC TextGeneration<br/>Auth: mTLS optional
    Runtime->>TextGenLocal: Dispatch to module (in-process)
    TextGenLocal->>TextGenLocal: HuggingFace model inference<br/>(PyTorch, in-process)
    TextGenLocal-->>Runtime: Generated text response
    Runtime-->>Client: JSON / gRPC response

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 2: Remote TGIS Text Generation Inference

    Client->>Runtime: POST /api/v1/task/text-generation<br/>or gRPC TextGeneration<br/>Auth: mTLS optional
    Runtime->>TextGenTGIS: Dispatch to TGIS module (in-process)
    TextGenTGIS->>TGIS: gRPC GenerateRequest<br/>Port: 8033/TCP<br/>Encryption: TLS/mTLS optional
    TGIS-->>TextGenTGIS: GenerateResponse
    TextGenTGIS-->>Runtime: Generated text response
    Runtime-->>Client: JSON / gRPC response

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 3: Embedding / Reranking Inference

    Client->>Runtime: POST /api/v1/task/embedding<br/>or gRPC Embedding<br/>Auth: mTLS optional
    Runtime->>EmbedMod: Dispatch to module (in-process)
    EmbedMod->>EmbedMod: sentence-transformers inference<br/>(PyTorch, in-process)
    EmbedMod-->>Runtime: Embedding vectors
    Runtime-->>Client: JSON / gRPC response

    Note over Client,HFHub: Flow 4: PEFT Prompt Tuning (Training)

    Client->>Runtime: gRPC Training.Train()<br/>Port: 8085/TCP<br/>Auth: mTLS optional
    Runtime->>PeftTrain: PeftPromptTuning.train() (in-process)
    PeftTrain->>HFHub: Download base model/tokenizer<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>Auth: Bearer Token optional
    HFHub-->>PeftTrain: Model artifacts
    PeftTrain->>TorchDist: Distributed training<br/>TCP 29550/TCP (master_port)<br/>No encryption
    TorchDist-->>PeftTrain: Training complete
    PeftTrain-->>Runtime: Trained prompt vectors (.pt)
    Runtime-->>Client: Training response
